<paragraph id="71B73A7F7AEE58C583A77DD6B069AE93" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
COLOMBIA, 
<normalizedToken id="FB6A37AF66A2C54DA4239CD908D24437" originalValue="Chocó">Choco</normalizedToken>
: Alto de Buey, 500-1200 m a.s.l., 8 Jan 1973, 
<emphasis id="C6D2DC4B43C1C4711E8C036CA5488AA2" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Gentry, A.H. &amp; Forero, E. 7286</emphasis>
